data.name: AlertBox7.Text
data.value: This alert dialog appears only when you are modifying resources of a PE file (*.dll, *.exe, ...) that is a part of Windows system. If PE file is not located in any subfolder of %windir%, modifications will be made automatically without remembering these preferences and without showing alert dialog

data.name: alertBox24.Text
data.value: It is a service that listens to Windows events, and plays sounds according to the received event. It is used as a deflection method for charger connection/disconnection sounds (for any version of Windows) and logoff, logon, lock, unlock, shutdown sounds (in Windows 8 and higher).
